115
00:06:48,783 --> 00:06:50,660
Eh, Mihee-<i>ah,</i>
ayo pergi ke sana.

116
00:06:50,743 --> 00:06:51,744
Oke.

117
00:06:54,914 --> 00:06:55,832
Kitty, aku minta maaf.

118
00:06:55,915 --> 00:06:58,042
Segalanya berputar begitu saja,
